            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page4');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page4",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Siempre encuentra cosas raras y se entusiasma con sus descubrimientos."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page5');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page5",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "En fin, acabo de recibir un correo suyo diciendo que esta vez es de verdad."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page6');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page6",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Es intrigante, pero estamos ocupados con nuestra investigación de Pokémon."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page7');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page7",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "¿Podrías investigarlo por nosotros?"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page8');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page8",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Te daré un Pokémon como compañero. Todos son Pokémon raros que acabamos de encontrar."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page9');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page9",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Adelante. ¡Elige uno!"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Close",
                        "value": "close",
                        "action": [
                            "q.dialogue.close();",
                            "q.run_command('execute as ' + q.player.username + ' run pokerestart');",
                            "q.run_command('tag ' + q.player.username + ' add Dialogue3');",
                            "q.run_command('tag ' + q.player.username + ' remove InDialogue');"
                            ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        }
        ]
    }